reviewText: Anyone that wants to improve their marriage or want to get married in the future will find this series of 5 "lessons" of great value.  Our church showed these to anyone interested, and we had some good discussions following each one.
Jimmy Evans is so down to earth and so enjoyable to listen to!! Someone my husband can relate to. Loved it!!

This was a very valuable and informative learning tool. My husband who has resisted working on our Marriage enjoyed it and says he actually likes Jimmy Evans! It made a huge inpact I believe on my husband. Thank you and Bless you both, Jimmy and Karen!!
